                                            <br>
                                            The display values are splitted into two the ones that affect how the container behaves with others around it i.e <span class="extra">block</span>, <span class="extra">inline-block</span>, <span class="extra">inline</span> and the ones that affect the behaviour of containers within it i.e <span class="extra">flex</span>, <span class="extra">grid</span>
                                            <br>
